original: Åhlström, Carl Erik Rudolf, härads-skrivare, Kisa, f. 7/2/99 i Klock-rike, östergötl. 1., av Rudolf Johansson o. Hanna Åhlström. G. 27 m. Ingegerd Linden. Barn: Gunnel f. 28, Bo-Bertil 31, Anne-Marie 37. — Stud:ex. 19, kanshex. 24. Anst. v. länsstyr. i östergötl. 1. fr. 24, ord. landskont. fr. 32, häradsskriv. i Kin-da o. Ydre fögd. fr. 43.
translated: Åhlström, Carl Erik Rudolf, district clerk, Kisa, born 7/2/99 in Klockrike, Östergötland. Son of Rudolf Johansson and Hanna Åhlström. Married on 27 m. to Ingegerd Linden. Children: Gunnel, born in 1928, Bo-Bertil, born in 1931, Anne-Marie, born in 1937. Graduated from studentexamen in 1919, kansliexamen in 1924. Employed by the county board in Östergötland 1 since 1924, became a regular landskontor official in 1932, and district clerk in Kin-da and Ydre fögd from 1943 onwards.
